  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether powdered ginger root (encapsulated ginger)
      is effective for reducing the frequency, duration and severity of both acute and delayed
      nausea and vomiting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
